Uses of Interface
net.objectzoo.delegates.Action4

  • Packages that use Action4 
    Package Description
    net.objectzoo.delegates
    This package contains the delegates of the Events4J API.
    net.objectzoo.delegates.adapters
    This package contains support classes that can be used to wrap standard delegates to be asynchronous.
    net.objectzoo.delegates.impl
    This package contains support classes that can be used to implement AsyndAction or AsyncFunction delegates.
    net.objectzoo.events
    This package contains the events of the Events4J API.
    net.objectzoo.events.impl
    This package contains support classes that implement EventDelegates ready to be used.

      interface  Event4AsyncDelegate<T1,T2,T3,T4>
      An Event4AsyncDelegate implements Action4Async as well as Event4Delegate and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action4Async interface asynchronously to all subscribers of the Event4Delegate interface.
      interface  Event4Delegate<T1,T2,T3,T4>
      An Event4Delegate implements Action4 as well as Event4 and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action4 interface to all subscribers of the Event4 interface.
